m創辦人兼CEO杜羅夫（IG@durov）\"><figcaption>Telegram創辦人兼CEO杜羅夫（IG@durov）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20250620/1012690318077726720349517.jpeg/zsWDehHzcYwc7mrN_QPN0QBkhAXPoLtQQjos00I6LNM\" alt=\"Telegram創辦人兼CEO杜羅夫（IG@durov）\"><figcaption>Telegram創辦人兼CEO杜羅夫（IG@durov）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20250620/1012690320183398400356907.jpeg/N04sX-C3VwG2zAz5nE00yIGC4DA5HS6joognqaKIJ6k\" alt=\"Telegram創辦人兼CEO杜羅夫（IG@durov）\"><figcaption>Telegram創辦人兼CEO杜羅夫（IG@durov）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20250620/1012690322326818816697503.jpeg/fNBj6Z7F0WxdaDLerjzJgVxO4XtfKbi94YG7N-GBuzc\" alt=\"Telegram創辦人兼CEO杜羅夫（IG@durov）\"><figcaption>Telegram創辦人兼CEO杜羅夫（IG@durov）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20250620/1012690324482822144058917.jpeg/bYNzuAD_vK6aUeuPsX2Pi2hStfX_x0uLqVo3xKlaN8Q\" alt=\"Telegram創辦人兼CEO杜羅夫（IG@durov）\"><figcaption>Telegram創辦人兼CEO杜羅夫（IG@durov）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20250620/1012690326584299520461520.jpeg/0Ij0it7j5vVGxCvHLymAUDhIHgQKuDkn3l3lAt5d5QI\" alt=\"Telegram創辦人兼CEO杜羅夫（IG@durov）\"><figcaption>Telegram創辦人兼CEO杜羅夫（IG@durov）</figcaption></figure><p>居住在國外的杜羅夫當時批評，俄方的指控旨在打壓言論自由，「一個國家害怕自己的人民，這真是令人悲哀的景象。」</p></body></html>","scraped_at":"2026-04-22T20:43:32.024350+00:00","quality":{"score":2,"chars":803,"images":21,"source":"HK01 國際","fallback":"none"}}